      <title>阿塞拜疆审判纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫地区亚美尼亚前领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/azerbaijan-puts-armenian-ex-leaders-of-nagorno-karabakh-on-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前莫斯科投资银行家鲁本·瓦尔达尼扬和其他 15 名曾争夺纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫地区的亚美尼亚领导人于周五在阿塞拜疆接受审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/azerbaijan-puts-armenian-ex-leaders-of-nagorno-karabakh-on-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 14:51:38 GMT</pubDate>
